  "body": "**Steps to Reproduce**\r\nIn order to replicate the behavior, please provide a detailed list of steps:\r\n1. Set PivotNumber to 17501000\r\n2. Set AncientBodiesBarrier and AncientReceiptsBarrier to 17801000\r\n3. Start a node with AutoPivot\r\n4. Ensure AutoPivot would work and pick some recent finalized block for example 18020000\r\n5. Wait for OldBodies/OldReceipts\r\n\r\n**Actual behavior**\r\nOldBodies and OldReceipts syncs to 17501000 when it should to 17801000.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n1. OldBodies and OldReceipts should be set to 17801000.\r\n2. In scenario where AutoPivot number would be 18020000 and Barriers would be set to something higher like 18120000 then ancient barriers should be updated to 18020000 \r\n\r\n[EDIT] - second scenario is nice to be added as a protection for other unexpected issue when we start bodies/receipts with barrier higher than chain head but in reality this is big edge case and someone in that case should use NonValidator mode since it may mean that user just did not want to have receipts/bodies at all.\r\n\r\n**Logs**\r\nLogs from user on Discord:\r\n[mainnet.logs (3).txt](https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/files/12466651/mainnet.logs.3.txt)\r\n\r\n\r\n",
